It took me like a year and a half, probably 800+ hours, but it was still worth it.<br>
<br>
Who has one?<br>
Most of the older warriors in my guild<br>
<br>
What is your haste?<br>
Lousy 21% when I got it, was still good. Most of the other warriors had 30~% haste and it was fine for them. Now have 41% haste and its even better (still use red in offhand)<br>
<br>
Did it make a difference to you and the guild for tanking?<br>
Huge difference, we got 4 of them in a relatively short time, much easier to hold argo with them.<br>
<br>
How do you use it (ie which combo do you use, or with which weapons do you use it for best results)?<br>
Replaced the blue one day after I got it with a 14/20 from Ssara (crappy lure FR debuff proc, 0 argo). Use red almost always in offhand, have stolen argo maybe 10 times, and only about 3 times when it resulted in me dieing. Only use the blue if I get 2-3 procs quickly and I'm not MT or I think I'm gonna have to tank anytime soon.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=485.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=485.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=485.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=485.topic&index=21><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=485.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.threadControl?topicID=485.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=485.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topic